dialog.body: Hello, thank you for calling Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jordan Sanchez. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Helen. Can you please confirm your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
My policy number is five eight two three four six and my date of birth is one two zero three one nine eight seven.
Thank you, Helen. I also need your current address to update our records. Could you provide me with your full address including street number, street name, city, and zip code?
Sure, my address is one two three Main Street, Sunnydale, 9 zero zero zero one.
Great, your address has been updated. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Helen?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Helen. If you have any further questions, feel free to contact us. Have a great day!
Thank you for calling Old Stone Auto Insurance. Goodbye.
